      <title>The Variety of Ways You Can Improve Your Life With Hatha Yoga</title>
      <link>http://allyogazone.com/the-variety-of-ways-you-can-improve-your-life-with-hatha-yoga</link>
      <comments>http://allyogazone.com/the-variety-of-ways-you-can-improve-your-life-with-hatha-yoga#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Jan 2009 13:36:45 +0000</pubDate>
